  "subject": "[POLICY] Disable clamp CSIT job for policy/docker",
  "commit_message": "[POLICY] Disable clamp CSIT job for policy/docker\n\nThe CSIT suite for clamp has been relocated from policy/docker\nrepo to policy/clamp repo. policy/clamp jobs have already been\nupdated to run CSITs on each commit (review verification job).\nThis commit disables clamp CSITs for policy/docker repo.\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-5513\nSigned-off-by: danielhanrahan <daniel.hanrahan@est.tech>\nChange-Id: Id7f0b391897e59a3633f8da0284d970d72f2b44a\n",
